name: Twister Finance
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Lending and borrowing platform on Arbitrum

What makes your project unique?
We utilize assets that generate high yield as collateral allowing capital efficiency.

History of your project.
We have been building for the last 3 months and released a beta of our platform 2 weeks ago.

What’s next for your project?
we will be adding new markets weekly to attract new users to the platform. 

What can your token be used for?
It will be used to stake and earn a portion of the revenue generated from the protocol.
